# CLAUDE.md

**BeFirst_Docs** - Single source of truth for BeFirst Manufacturing Intelligence Platform documentation.

## Core Principles

- ✅ **Everything in Git** - All documentation assets version controlled here
- ✅ **Deliverables committed** - Generated HTML, PDF, DOCX committed to `deliverables/`
- ✅ **Self-contained** - No external dependencies (OneDrive, file shares)
- ❌ **No parallel documentation** - This repo is the single source

## Quick Start

```bash
# Clone and setup
git clone <repository-url>
cd BeFirst_Docs

# Create Python virtual environment
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1  # Windows
source venv/bin/activate    # macOS/Linux

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Build documentation
python scripts/build_docs.py --config complete-docs

# Deactivate when done
deactivate
```

**See `docs/08_SETUP.md` for detailed setup and `docs/09_TROUBLESHOOTING.md` for common issues.**

## Platform Overview

**BeFirst Platform**: 13-repository manufacturing intelligence ecosystem for Safari Circuits

**Architecture:**
```
PLEX ERP (Source) → ETL (Talend) → 4 Databases → APIs/Services → Portal/Apps
```

**Key Components:**
- **6 Application Repos**: Portal (ASP.NET MVC 5), APIs (.NET Core 7.0), Services (VB.NET), Desktop apps
- **4 Database Repos**: PROD_DWH (49 tables), MES (824 tables), MACHINES_RESULTS (22), TESTERS_RESULTS (4)
- **1 ETL Repo**: Talend Open Studio (40+ modules)
- **1 Reporting Repo**: SSRS (54+ dashboards)
- **1 Documentation Repo**: **BeFirst_Docs (this repo)**

**Facilities:** GRA1 (Granby, QC), JUA1/JUA2 (Ciudad Juárez, Mexico)

**See `docs/02_ARCHITECTURE.md` for complete architecture details.**

